OL,5, The experience of being a black woman  
OL,6, in the police in Bristol has changed   
OL,7, drastically in the past 40 years.      
OL,9,FHere three black women - Beverley      
OL,10,FDouglas, the first black female Special
OL,11,FConstable, Adora Pomphrey, the first   
OL,12,Ffemale black police officer in the     
OL,13,Fforce, and Ayesha Giles, who is the    
OL,14,Fcurrent most senior officer - talk to  
OL,15,FOsob Elmi about their experiences.     
OL,17,FBeverley Douglas joined Avon and       
OL,18,FSomerset police in 1983 and, after more
OL,19,Fthan three decades, she retired in     
OL,20,F2017.                                  
